on**\n\nI'm thinking about how to create the `InstrumentedSocket` by extending `Socket` and overriding the connect method. It seems simpler to have a factory method that increments a static `AtomicInteger` in `getDefault/createSocket`. The native implementation doesn't pose an issue, but I need to ensure that my test isn't in the same package since it's `javax.mail.mail`. I also need to cover the `Class.forName` aspect and consider what happens if the context classloader is null. I'll look into how `SocketFetcher` uses `AccessController` for that.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_07fdd8ed298c7a6e0169f5040d6f848194b2ee02ce18bed10a\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp9QQcIhI6IfUajsW3iT8Z1tOLHp67riRSJASP6UpQM55dHToBjFhV8EWOBiU2ddrOtLQJQbz4IRAo23LaUlTdTZWEZq7RW6i7Y0pSBa4Sx_XXBagpUaBp42qLBrmYIt6sHdPtLgrgev6sCjwPJl6J9lHTM9cZJuWUc1FLwwzJbrgAzqSQe8zz5h4INTXMI4JgGKOGr4ibknbwXKKFN6bmCT0UhgG_MGHaOjbIU3OCm33SaLhHqNgJVTTexTz47P1s5Y6YUsPKzOnvSSmMRpEIsLpklhCigUnlkljdkD3tk0qWiOqJSJ4xMBuI1cqoDOjHAmRQ95RsWHXkHMR0GNy-1xspKrXMxzOFj38sEYIUYLrZCsCDc_80fFYsF4dpbcX2bA_k-kV_HPYz42lSfJX89DAN_ntmnCEkWTBr6t7c0lfXt5EfLSFJMr9_Blqq5lohs8KWdJwPa6a9kEuKJGMj_ydMm3zx_3zHDT7tumUQIdozrtmK2GNRWqCtGbFKcK6xixzwsxOScGv03YWtX-gi4ssRU0v64J7R-SKGJ4w4QZchYPrRROAfB1aoch6mGeMKwacgrROc8depWpLkNpUp7GIGkcugnbGngSm0g1iwX0mYO1fX-esjQaldKCc50XH7rsdLyzuWdBz-mr-Gvvq2KIefu45IDbM95nWzMfjx89ziXkhgfq4jj454eYjH5u4VVV8By6w1lJUbUQuvSAxsiG1aj3EuGFNKvlmlL-9pK95FvhSZGzw_4hGqPWeErA8hTI6SsGMBiBOqH3q9Woy_CcFOqUZ0eDalI57wxHVCKKniSRst6m9AWEB-xRzEK2RNF-5_flLjMv-1O4ydtKkLd3pc-8wn9w9oJ9akWWGd2hY5e9q_FPNRaqUW_LMKqpJQTlu6cboTsqyBXMZ6GhbsVShoQ45O6MSxRIo9gRe-CnewcAznFVy5tRdr7A8TxRkR_85RDtb5qtbW_MgAXeVmO7IStP33zbfQ_H1C6QUZfj2MPuMpPdBiw5M70QYA4YE7-spXlqjjluz8ArU4o2lBvVSMVID7i3_9u6QX5QeEpn38v5crRGF7boCZcMC0IqVxSiqids5-S31qt9DXfRPfA2R_R2hQy9brUOJCgH-UdO42n5RA-ELLoV2Wi49W_20AHOqsVgspeb5jbzSiCwOcXpVjJ53BYIS_9D0DX0HO8yalWxKWgKvcCnMz7jT4L9jbfQVg71MXm_pqihqlMioIPS275bKmVBM_jA01QbcW9RZUDp3-gWkxAr8eZhCgMe_iLW3g4Ke3A-HqI5lM7Eo5V